Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:23.21,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}褪色的景致 隨著風兒逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:31.01,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,往日記憶 悄悄甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.93,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,走在熟悉的路上卻無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}最初的謊言 最後的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:57.45,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那天許下的誓言早已崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.71,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下激昂虛幻的記憶碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:12.67,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們一同從這夢境中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:18.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}這份思念 也不會被忘記 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.69,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}懷念的往昔照亮今天的我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:21.90,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那時還年幼的我 抬頭仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:28.28,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,發現天空真的很遼闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.78,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人 用雙手保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:38.71,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經認真的這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:50.18,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有長高 我為此而悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:53.43,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾無數次伸展手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:00.81,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,卻還是無法觸及 那無比寬廣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:06.73,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻沒有一絲懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:11.66,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,始終堅信那美好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.91,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾有過悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.33,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,亦會忍不住落下 大滴大滴的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:33.47,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}但是我堅信 那時我的眼中有著無比的光輝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位市民 這裡是聯邦空軍宣傳部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在南埃萊斯附近出現了光粒子的異常聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大氣上層產生了大規模積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子總量無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家迅速在空軍的指揮下進行避難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計將會出現大規模災害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是聯邦空軍宣傳部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 該你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終式也一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Into The Nature
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡的狀態好像還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要下雪了吧 你竟然會擔心優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是霍蘭德在擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體沒有問題 各種數值都很穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是精神原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 也就是沒幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神要是得了病 也有可能臥床不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和尼爾瓦修不能很好地配合成了她的心病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的原因麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是尼爾瓦修的原因?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是優萊卡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思蒙多吉 把沙拉醬給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我正要放棄的時候 突然聽到了我甜心的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就把蜂擁而上的海盜全給打趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意思的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也做了個好夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蒙多吉約會的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夜裡突然渾身動彈不得 出了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢到了去滑空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘風破浪 舒服極了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太普通了 沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡最近夢見什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒做過夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 正好大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊吃邊聽也可以 這是很重要的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 優萊卡 你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 待會兒我告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 科拉利安來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是件大事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏實點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科拉利安是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上 南埃萊斯周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方圓100公里的范圍內被定為禁飛區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且光粒子全部向中心流動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子流甚至在月光號上都能觀測到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就毫無疑問了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心有科拉利安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南埃萊斯離這裡很近啊 馬上就能到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 所以決定先接近它 確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果錯過這次機會 不知道什麼時候還會再出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要干麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機倒沒什麼不好 但是優萊卡的那個樣子我不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞的情況下 靠我們自己也要干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 科拉利安到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不舒服 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是零式的發動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是想不到會出現在塔的正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況下必須要考慮難民的收容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俱胝級的科拉利安上一次出現已經是多少年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情勢已經轉向新的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 杜伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 但這同時也是個絕好的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們如果不出現反而不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就沒法踏出殲滅的這第一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科拉利安…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挨個問了每個人 但誰也沒說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是神 而我就是曾經無限接近神的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用管這個 先去把衣服晾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不清楚 但是好像很厲害呦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一種大波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種無法再次嘗試的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神之座 是通往高一層意識的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類向前進化所必經的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科拉利安?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為它大家都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什麼是科拉利安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴你了是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這次你看家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身體還沒完全恢復 我們幾個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 沒有我誰去進入通道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 雖然我不很清楚 不過你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶這小子去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果她出了什麼事我可不放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 你剛才不是說不讓她去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 身體不好為什麼還要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是霍蘭德的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會跟我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然憋氣 但我只能點頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從對話來看 她們以前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎對那個科拉利安做過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上出發去南埃萊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要跟你討論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實你的軍階更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是作為參謀從總部派來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個開關 干什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是緊急情況下使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常用這兩個轉盤來進行聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什麼呢 快關上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 瞎胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還要請你讓出你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給安妮莫奈使用 這是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫加利巴 帶它在船上轉轉吧 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到歸隊後的第一個任務是帶寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 我來幫您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認輸 我不會服輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 媽媽沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要走麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去了 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會回來的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雲彩是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是科拉利安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態還比較穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修 別發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎 我沒有啊 沒發抖…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在準備進入那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修和斯托納開606 希爾德開808開路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠光粒子滑行氣流引導尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了保存優萊卡的體力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後等再次接近通道的時候 尼爾瓦修突入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也隨後跟進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尼爾瓦修上待機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒跟我報告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也明白吧 她就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還可以呆在房間裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我討厭屋裡那大叔的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我頭直疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俱胝102 位置不變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子流入量在繼續增大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那玩意 非起個俱胝這種無聊的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人都是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒有 KLF第三小隊馬上做好出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標的再確認和戰鬥力的保持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上學的時候沒學過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按參謀大人的指示去做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一行為恕我記錄在案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了呢 為什麼不高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 優萊卡 身體還是不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒關係 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子濃度上升了30%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持現在的速度和高度嘗試接近俱胝102
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 注意控制機體姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發抖呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 別瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音都啞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人 我這是因為興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來808
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾瓦修也出動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記著我的話呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記著呢 霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子濃度比預想的還高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波浪像岩石一樣硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適應了就好了 頂多是反作用大了點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修 高度再降低一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有光線射入的話構圖會很美的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡來了 我保持正常姿勢就很費勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真外行 藝術就是要有獻身精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子濃度上升了20% 機體姿勢無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度不要太快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信官 每隔30秒向他們發出測量信息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25 30 40 50
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子濃度還在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01 02 兩機均消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,03消失 第三小隊全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神之座 無法再次嘗試的體驗 難以表達的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往高一層意識的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我頭疼沒法集中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 絕對不要 我頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想出擊 不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 我頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俱胝102後方發現戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 識別結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性82% SL-1200 Mk-II
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是月光號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 全體備戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科拉利安的另一側有聯邦軍的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏這種時候出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡還沒有到達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 突入通道之前不能讓人打擾她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體進入戰斗準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊 我還以為又要逃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續計算光粒子濃度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有和科拉利安的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終式正在急速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小姑娘在干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有更好的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,606 808 離通道還有30公里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身起了雞皮疙瘩 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴好好集中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色很不好 要不還是先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 看前邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修 調整步調保持一致
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,606被擊偏 有不明機體正向高空移動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回收606 基傑特 聯繫尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子太濃 無法通信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想成真了 我的甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜什麼啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾瓦修 我要先返回月光號
